      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 2,
      "text": "<TemplateList>\n\n  [+ New Draft]  [Sync from Meta]\n\n  Status [v]   Tier [v]   Search...\n\n  [APPROVED] welcome_message  -  en\n  [APPROVED] order_confirmation  -  en\n  [APPROVED] order_tracking  -  en\n  [PENDING ] thank_you_v2  -  en\n  [DRAFT   ] snow_white_v3  -  en\n  [REJECTED] catalog_intro  -  en",
      "textAlign": "center",
